---
title: Savoury Mushrooms, Leeks and Spinach with Creamy Roasted Veggie Mash and Almonds
description: There's nothing better than meaty mushrooms sautéed with leeks and spinach in an umami rich sauce. Layer it all over a creamy mash of roasted sweet potatoes and squash for a gorgeous, restaurant-worthy dish that you just pulled off in your own kitchen!
